@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #NOT_REQUIRED
@EndUserText.label: 'Vehicle Inward Item BO View Interface'
define view entity ZWBI_I_VEHIN_ITEM
  as select from zwbi_vin_i as _Item //zdt_vehin_item as _Item
  association to parent ZWBI_I_VEHIN_HEAD as _Head on $projection.Inward_uuid = _Head.Inward_Uuid

{
  key item_uuid             as Item_Uuid, 
  key inward_uuid           as Inward_uuid,
      inwarditem            as Inwarditem,
      ordnum                as Ordnum,
      orderdate             as Orderdate,
      bpcode                as Bpcode,
      bpname                as Bpname,
      brokername            as Brokername,
      quantity              as Quantity,
      grossweight           as GrossWeight,
      netweight             as NetWeight,
      intype                as Intype,
      dchannel              as Dchannel,
      plant                 as Plant, 
      planttext             as Planttext,
      unit                  as Unit,
      itemunit              as Itemunit,
      pickquantity          as Pickquantity,
      packquantity          as Packquantity,
      overalldbstatus       as Overalldbstatus,
      overallgoodsmovstatus as Overallgoodsmovstatus,
      overallpackstatus     as Overallpackstatus,
      overallpickconfstatus as Overallpickconfstatus,
      overallpickstatus     as Overallpickstatus,
      shippoint             as Shippoint,
      shipptext             as Shipptext,
      dunit                 as Dunit,
      podelvstatus          as Podelvstatus,
      isfinallyinvoiced     as Isfinallyinvoiced,
      sloc                  as Sloc,            
      sloctext              as Sloctext,    
      invquantity           as Invquantity,
      delquantity           as Delquantity,  
      stilltodelquantity    as Stilltodelquantity,  
      delqty                as Delqty, //01-06
 //     unit                  as Uom,   //17-05          
//      @Semantics.user.createdBy: true
      created_by            as CreatedBy,
      created_on            as CreatedOn,
//      @Semantics.user.lastChangedBy: true
      last_changed_by       as LastChangedBy,
      @Semantics.systemDateTime.localInstanceLastChangedAt: true
      local_last_changed_at as LocalLastChangedAt,
  //     _Planttext.PlantName  as Plantdesc, 
      _Head
//  _Planttext
}
